Text: 'The story began with my breakup. When i was not mature enough to understand
  what the breakup was. But i did suffer that. That the third year of my engineering
  from electronics and communication engineering with cooperative faculty i was alone.

  There was always n headache but i had never drunk. Once i thought to drink but my
  soul refused saying not for a girl who left you.

  On the very second thought i left the glass of whiskey and'
